  [Text] President Fidel Castro received Fausto Alzadi, who 
is in Havana to sign a scientific and technical research accord 
between the Mexican National Council for Science and Technology 
and Cuba's State Committee for Economic Cooperation [CECE]. 
During the meeting between our commander in chief and the 
Mexican visitor an exchange of opinions took place regarding the 
development of bilateral ties in research fields and application 
of research in economic and scientific development programs. 
