  [Text] There was a brief conversation on the morning of 19 
April between the U.S. ambassador to Port-au-Prince and three 
officials of extreme-right organizations of lesser importance, 
including the Convergence of Mass Organizations, the Haitian 
Front for Democratic and Nationalist Organizations, and the 
Haitian People's Alliance. Those officials asked the Americans 
