  [Text] During the provincial meeting to summarize the 
workers parliaments in Matanzas Province, Ricardo Alarcon de 
Quesada, president of the National Assembly of the People's 
Government, stated that only the people can work economic 
miracles. Alarcon stated that no law can accomplish the miracles 
