  [Text] [Reporter] General Corado, what can you tell us 
about the election? 
  [Corado] I came here to cast my vote and try to assess the 
Salvadoran people's participation in this run-off election, 
where I think there will be a clear winner. 
  [Reporter] What about the number of people participating? 
  [Corado] The number of voters is considerable. There are 
