<F P=106> [Report from the Ramada Inn Hotel in San Salvador by Angel </F>
Iraheta -- live] 
  [Text] [Iraheta] We are here at the Ramada Inn Hotel, where 
Dr. Ruben Zamora has just confirmed that he telephoned 
presidential candidate Dr. Armando Calderon Sol to congratulate 
him. Let us listen to Dr. Ruben Zamora, presidential candidate 
