<F P=100> Colombia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Reaction to Drug Trafficker's Testimony </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Reaction to Drug Trafficker's Testimony </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA2304200394 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Canal 
