<H3> <TI>   Defense Minister Reacts to Taboada Remarks </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Defense Minister Reacts to Taboada Remarks </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA2304030194 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Canal 
